-- Telecom Italia Suspends Planned Job Cuts as Part of Union Negotiations
-- Marco Bertacche
-- 2010-07-14T17:31:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/telecom-italia-suspends-planned-job-cuts-as-part-of-union-negotiations.html

          
          
             Telecom Italia SpA suspended planned
job cuts as part of on-going negotiations with labor unions,
according to an e-mailed statement from the Slc-Cgil union.  
          
          


  


        